WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.199 --> 00:00:01.177
Good morning, family.

00:00:01.177 --> 00:00:02.886
How are y'all doing today?

00:00:02.886 --> 00:00:04.508
Well, praise the Lord!

00:00:04.508 --> 00:00:06.151
I'm excited to be here today.

00:00:06.151 --> 00:00:09.818
I have some things on my heart we're going to pray about.

00:00:10.120 --> 00:00:19.399
You know, a lot of people—I guess I caused some confusion on not the last video, but the video before—people are asking, "What are you talking about, the economy?

00:00:19.399 --> 00:00:22.205
I thought it was going to crash and all this stuff.

00:00:22.205 --> 00:00:34.749
" I saw when President Trump wins the election, the economy and the news of winning causes a ripple throughout the whole world.

00:00:35.755 --> 00:00:40.524
There are a lot of people that will be excited; yes, there will be a lot of people that are not excited.

00:00:40.524 --> 00:00:51.971
But for the most part, what I was shown was that there is an economic—like people, when they hear the news, the stock market rallies and gets excited and things happen.

00:00:51.971 --> 00:00:54.434
I saw a pumping of the economy.

00:00:54.434 --> 00:00:57.880
And so people were like, "I thought you said you saw the economy crash?

00:00:57.880 --> 00:01:00.039
" I did, and I still do.

00:01:00.039 --> 00:01:03.060
I told you all that it was like a house of cards.

00:01:03.900 --> 00:01:09.703
I saw the BRICS nations rising up and trying to create their digital platform.

00:01:09.703 --> 00:01:14.000
I said, "I believe this is me looking into a vision.

00:01:14.000 --> 00:01:28.280
" Whenever I've said this, there is depth perception in a vision where you are looking, whether it's a year, a month, or two years or whatever; it's very hard to tell.

00:01:28.280 --> 00:01:29.249
You have to...

00:01:29.249 --> 00:01:34.760
it's like this: the Lord told me, "You are going to have to be so precise.

00:01:34.760 --> 00:01:40.017
It's going to be like a ticking of a clock when it comes to investments.

00:01:41.686 --> 00:01:45.420
" He said because if you're too early, you're too early; if you're too late, you're too late.

00:01:46.320 --> 00:01:48.015
You have to be just like a clock.

00:01:48.015 --> 00:01:51.340
He was referring in my heart because my favorite watch is a Rolex.

00:01:51.340 --> 00:01:54.585
I've never owned one, but I think they're beautiful.

00:01:54.585 --> 00:02:00.980
And he talked to me about how precise a tick is: tick, tick, tick, tick, tick.

00:02:03.079 --> 00:02:03.502
Invest.

00:02:03.502 --> 00:02:03.925
Tick, tick, tick.

00:02:04.770 --> 00:02:05.616
Don't invest.

00:02:05.616 --> 00:02:13.644
If you do it by the precision of the heartbeat of the Father, you will not miss it.

00:02:13.644 --> 00:02:18.180
But if you're doing it too early, it is too early in investments.

00:02:18.180 --> 00:02:30.776
If you get in there and you invest too early and he's not saying that yet, and you put something into something, then you could lose money, right?

00:02:31.152 --> 00:02:35.000
Or it could be way too early or whatever.

00:02:35.630 --> 00:02:42.943
And then all of a sudden he says, "Invest in this," and you are scared to invest in it because your flesh is involved.

00:02:42.943 --> 00:02:46.005
And he's saying, "Do something," and you're going, "Man, I don't know.

00:02:46.005 --> 00:02:50.920
" And then it shoots up really high and you miss the opportunity to put your money in it.

00:02:50.920 --> 00:03:01.890
And so that's why I'm saying it has to be you, when you are doing stuff with money, hearing his voice right on every single thing.

00:03:01.890 --> 00:03:25.141
So whenever I tell you the Lord is telling me a season of grace, a time of grace, he said, "Brandon, there has been much prayer that has gone before me over the month of October, and I am granting more grace over what I would see was going to be hell on earth.

00:03:25.141 --> 00:03:28.200
" There was like a small little window.

00:03:29.560 --> 00:03:34.930
Now, what that entails—if that's until the first of the year, a small window—I have no idea.

00:03:34.930 --> 00:03:40.660
Ladies and gentlemen, I'm human, and when I'm praying, I'm just telling you exactly what I'm seeing.

00:03:40.660 --> 00:03:43.933
And so I want you to pray about it too.

00:03:43.933 --> 00:03:50.009
It's not for you to ride on the back and just go, "Hey, you figure it out, Brother Brandon.

00:03:50.009 --> 00:03:50.333
" No, no, no.

00:03:50.982 --> 00:03:51.956
You help me.

00:03:51.956 --> 00:03:58.097
If I bring something to you to pray about and it doesn't witness with you, then say, "That doesn't sound like anything.

00:03:58.680 --> 00:04:00.640
That doesn't witness with my spirit at all.

00:04:00.640 --> 00:04:02.897
I don't believe you're hearing the Lord.

00:04:02.897 --> 00:04:03.493
" That's fine.

00:04:04.982 --> 00:04:07.168
We hear in part and we see in part.

00:04:07.168 --> 00:04:09.464
And so what I may see, you may not see.

00:04:09.464 --> 00:04:17.199
You know, a lot of people were like, "What did you pray about the New York Yankees and all that for so long?

00:04:17.199 --> 00:04:20.380
" I brought it up because the Lord brought it up to me.

00:04:20.380 --> 00:04:29.660
I saw the vision of the New York Yankees going to the World Series and the Los Angeles Dodgers clear back in like May.

00:04:30.275 --> 00:04:38.639
And I saw attempted attacks on Yankee Stadium, and he kept telling me, "Watch the Yankees.

00:04:38.639 --> 00:04:38.913
Watch the Yankees.

00:04:39.462 --> 00:04:44.022
" That's the only word he was giving me: "Watch and pray for the Yankees.

00:04:44.364 --> 00:04:49.280
" And so when you add to or take away from anything whenever he's talking to you...

00:04:49.280 --> 00:04:52.080
I'm just giving you what I'm learning.

00:04:52.440 --> 00:04:58.396
I'm thinking in my natural mind, even into August, and he says, "Pay attention to the Yankees.

00:05:01.253 --> 00:05:05.004
" I'm thinking, "Wow, the Yankees are going to go to the World Series and win it.

00:05:05.004 --> 00:05:08.514
" But he said it would be the Los Angeles Dodgers and the Yankees.

00:05:08.514 --> 00:05:11.840
So just like he said, it happened.

00:05:11.840 --> 00:05:21.980
So I'm at October, and I told the pastor, "Hey, I believe the Yankees are going to win," because we just talk sports.

00:05:21.980 --> 00:05:25.319
And so I'm seeing this at the prayer conference.

00:05:25.319 --> 00:05:34.184
Whenever I'm talking about this to the pastor, I'm going, "Well, you know, the Lord's been telling me to watch the Yankees since May.

00:05:34.184 --> 00:05:40.140
" I mean, this is a long time—that we pray over it, that there would be no attacks at the World Series, because I knew they were going to the World Series.

00:05:40.285 --> 00:05:44.812
I just had no idea if they were going to win.

00:05:44.812 --> 00:05:47.850
I saw them going, but then I saw Los Angeles.

00:05:47.850 --> 00:05:56.699
So when it got to the Friday when they started the game, the Lord says, "Los Angeles will win it in game five, the whole thing.

00:05:56.699 --> 00:05:59.851
" And I thought, "Game five, the whole thing?

00:05:59.851 --> 00:06:07.440
" But they'll have three games to pray over at Yankee Stadium that nothing happens.

00:06:07.440 --> 00:06:12.952
And that was, I believe, Monday, Tuesday, Wednesday.

00:06:16.950 --> 00:06:21.360
Three games in a row at Yankee Stadium, but they would lose in game five.

00:06:21.360 --> 00:06:22.953
And I was like, "Oh, wow.

00:06:23.749 --> 00:06:25.505
" Lord, I thought they were going to win.

00:06:25.505 --> 00:06:33.049
Not that it matters, but it's learning to listen to his voice.

00:06:33.049 --> 00:06:35.511
Do not assume anything.

00:06:36.383 --> 00:06:46.600
Do not think for him, thinking, "Well, I believe this is what you're saying.

00:06:46.600 --> 00:06:48.120
" Don't add to it.

00:06:48.120 --> 00:06:50.023
He said, "Pray for the Yankees.

00:06:50.023 --> 00:06:51.129
Pray for the stadium.

00:06:51.129 --> 00:06:51.876
Pray for this.

00:06:51.876 --> 00:06:59.120
" And here I am, you start adding to the prophetic word by saying, "Oh, the Yankees are going to win.

00:06:59.120 --> 00:07:03.160
" But when it got down to teaching me...

00:07:05.475 --> 00:07:11.483
I'm just letting you all in on something that I never let a lot of people in on, and I'm obviously going to let thousands in now.

00:07:11.784 --> 00:07:19.569
But this is how I learn, and this is how he teaches me to flow in my gift and how I see and hear.

00:07:19.964 --> 00:07:25.000
Because I'm a work in progress and I'm hearing things, this is how I do it.

00:07:25.000 --> 00:07:32.439
And so whenever the Lord is instructing me, you get pieces of the puzzle and you build yourself.

00:07:32.839 --> 00:07:38.348
You do not become a champion in anything without practice.

00:07:38.348 --> 00:07:40.365
I don't care who you are.

00:07:40.365 --> 00:07:49.354
If you think that you're just going to jump right out and be a LeBron James or a Michael Jordan in anything you do, it's impossible.

00:07:49.354 --> 00:07:50.520
You have to learn how to...

00:07:52.821 --> 00:08:11.319
when you're riding a bike, you learn just as much how to pick yourself up when you fall than you do whenever you are an amazing BMX biker, or a Joe Montana, or Troy Aikman, or Emmitt Smith, or somebody in sports that was the best at their level.

00:08:13.737 --> 00:08:22.716
You do not become a great until you practice in high school all the way up to college, and then you keep going.

00:08:22.716 --> 00:08:29.120
You do not become a great overnight, basically, in anything.

00:08:30.240 --> 00:08:37.080
And even listening to the voice of the Lord, you practice his presence.

00:08:37.080 --> 00:08:41.719
You practice, and when you fall, you pick yourself back up.

00:08:41.719 --> 00:08:45.420
You keep going and you go, "Well, man, I missed it big," whatever.

00:08:47.519 --> 00:08:50.547
I'm trying to paint a picture for you all.

00:08:50.547 --> 00:08:54.530
So here, I saw about the Yankees.

00:08:54.530 --> 00:09:04.079
So I'm assuming privately between my wife and I and my kids and my pastor that the Yankees were going to win.

00:09:04.079 --> 00:09:06.074
And this is just something that we just talked about privately.

00:09:06.074 --> 00:09:07.468
I never made it public.

00:09:07.856 --> 00:09:11.653
I just talked about this because I thought, "Man, the Yankees are going to win.

00:09:11.653 --> 00:09:12.147
This is cool.

00:09:12.476 --> 00:09:14.170
" And we'll watch it play out.

00:09:14.170 --> 00:09:24.439
So when it got down to that Friday when the World Series started, the Lord came to me and he said, "Brandon, Los Angeles will win it in game five.

00:09:24.439 --> 00:09:25.679
" And I said, "Wow.

00:09:25.679 --> 00:09:28.695
" I said, "The Yankees are only going to win one game?

00:09:29.125 --> 00:09:31.192
" So you just talk over things with the Lord.

00:09:31.440 --> 00:09:33.508
I just make a note of it.

00:09:33.508 --> 00:09:34.612
I tell my son.

00:09:34.612 --> 00:09:38.840
We archive it so we know, because this is me learning.

00:09:38.840 --> 00:09:46.666
And so it gets down to game five and the Yankees are up by like six points or whatever it was.

00:09:46.666 --> 00:09:47.604
It was a lot.

00:09:47.604 --> 00:09:49.875
And I thought, "Man, I've missed it.

00:09:50.613 --> 00:09:56.970
" And then all of a sudden, in the fifth inning, they started falling apart.

00:09:56.970 --> 00:10:04.383
And they blew a humongous lead with errors and dropping the ball and throwing the ball.

00:10:05.480 --> 00:10:07.205
It was just stupid plays.

00:10:07.550 --> 00:10:13.195
And they lost the lead in the fifth inning in game five.

00:10:13.195 --> 00:10:18.485
And so for you that don't care about sports, I'm just trying to...

00:10:19.580 --> 00:10:20.933
for people who want to learn.

00:10:25.520 --> 00:10:32.629
So it got down to game five and they blew the lead, and they lost the game.

00:10:33.960 --> 00:10:36.330
And it was just like the Lord said.

00:10:36.330 --> 00:10:41.320
But at the point whenever I'm looking into it in the natural, I'm thinking, "Man, I missed it.

00:10:41.320 --> 00:10:42.383
There's going to be a game six.

00:10:42.383 --> 00:10:50.560
" And I told my wife, "Surely I didn't miss both what the Lord said about the fifth game and who was going to win.

00:10:50.560 --> 00:10:54.640
" Because I assumed it was going to be the Yankees, like I said.

00:10:54.640 --> 00:10:57.828
And lo and behold, it happened just like the Lord said.

00:10:57.828 --> 00:11:08.110
And then he scolded me and he said, "Brandon, you can never think for me that this is what you're assuming that I'm saying.

00:11:08.110 --> 00:11:11.820
Never add to a word that I'm giving you.

00:11:11.820 --> 00:11:23.106
" This was a good example of what I'm trying to practice with you, trying for you to learn that whenever you are looking into a vision, you do not add to or take away from anything.

00:11:27.540 --> 00:11:27.894
He said, "Pray for the Yankees in the stadium.

00:11:27.894 --> 00:11:29.252
" It's exactly what he said.

00:11:29.252 --> 00:11:31.307
And he said, "I told you Los Angeles.

00:11:31.850 --> 00:11:35.146
" He said, "I never told you anything else about who would win.

00:11:35.146 --> 00:11:36.692
" I said, "You're right.

00:11:36.692 --> 00:11:39.920
" I just assumed because you kept telling me to watch the Yankees.

00:11:42.498 --> 00:11:45.404
And I learned something.

00:11:46.733 --> 00:11:55.337
Even at the level I am and what I'm hearing and seeing, I still have correction from the Father all the time telling me, "Brandon, you're off.

00:11:56.434 --> 00:12:00.560
You need to learn and you need to grow.

00:12:00.560 --> 00:12:07.065
" So you may say, "Brandon, you have it all together," and there's a lot of you that don't think I have it all together because I get the comments.

00:12:07.065 --> 00:12:10.480
But there's a lot of people that do and they put you on a pedestal.

00:12:10.480 --> 00:12:13.919
And I'm telling you, I'm a work in progress just like you.

00:12:13.919 --> 00:12:20.591
And yes, some people are further along in their walk with the Lord than others, but it just all takes a day-to-day.

00:12:22.724 --> 00:12:23.621
We all learn by trial and error.

00:12:29.173 --> 00:12:29.426
We all learn just like by riding a bike how to listen to him.

00:12:41.591 --> 00:12:41.822
And my thing is sports.

00:12:41.822 --> 00:12:43.820
We talk about sports all the time.

00:12:43.820 --> 00:12:46.983
We talk about who's going to win the NBA championships.

00:12:46.983 --> 00:12:49.680
We talk about the Super Bowl.

00:12:49.680 --> 00:13:02.260
He'll tell me way in advance who's going to win the Super Bowl, and I'll write it down and I'll keep it private between me and my kids and my wife.

00:13:12.448 --> 00:13:12.616
It's something I learned how to build off of.

00:13:20.620 --> 00:13:24.657
And even being so precise of something that I saw clear back in May—which is very hard to do in the natural—I still missed it in my heart and I walked away discouraged.

00:13:26.879 --> 00:13:31.220
I thought, "Well...

00:13:37.160 --> 00:13:37.439
" and I'm just being real with y'all.

00:13:38.615 --> 00:13:42.589
I think it's good to be real, not to be so hyper...

00:13:42.589 --> 00:13:44.490
I'm just real.

00:13:44.490 --> 00:13:48.431
So going back to what I saw about the economy.

00:13:48.431 --> 00:13:53.137
And so you say, "Well, you said the economy is going to crash.

00:13:53.137 --> 00:13:57.982
You said that the interest rates were going to be lowered in April and you missed it.

00:13:59.863 --> 00:14:01.377
" And I apologize; I told you all I did.

00:14:02.065 --> 00:14:06.692
I saw what I assumed was the deflating of the balloon.

00:14:13.914 --> 00:14:19.160
I saw the deflating of the balloon and I added to it, saying that the interest rates were going to come down.

00:14:19.160 --> 00:14:24.470
I saw numbers and I thought the interest rates were coming down.

00:14:24.470 --> 00:14:25.709
I missed it.

00:14:25.709 --> 00:14:29.300
Then I saw the summer months and I saw the housing market shaking.

00:14:40.296 --> 00:14:40.688
I saw the thin membrane shaking, shaking, shaking.

00:14:40.688 --> 00:14:47.760
Nothing happened for the interest rates until, I believe, it was September.

00:14:54.096 --> 00:15:01.325
And then I told you all that I saw the bubble pop in October, and there would be an event happen in October.

00:15:01.325 --> 00:15:03.950
So then the Lord says to me, "You're going to pray over the economy.

00:15:03.950 --> 00:15:05.569
" We're praying for 30 days.

00:15:07.426 --> 00:15:07.573
And he said, "Much prayer in Washington, all these places...

00:15:07.573 --> 00:15:09.050
prayer has gone up before my throne.

00:15:10.799 --> 00:15:15.955
" And now, I saw this: going into 2025, that there would be great economic distress, a dam breaking, all the stuff flowing behind the dam.

00:15:20.831 --> 00:15:22.981
And I still see it.

00:15:24.979 --> 00:15:25.239
I believe in my spirit...

00:15:25.239 --> 00:15:26.617
I'm going to tell you...

00:15:26.617 --> 00:15:38.949
because you're going to say, "I don't really care what you think.

00:15:38.949 --> 00:15:41.065
What does the Lord say?

00:15:41.065 --> 00:15:43.151
" This is how I do it.

00:15:43.151 --> 00:15:46.104
If you want to listen to the channel, fine.

00:15:46.104 --> 00:15:50.007
If you don't, go listen to somebody else, and that's fine.

00:15:50.007 --> 00:15:55.320
I'm not trying to sway you or twist your arm to be here.

00:15:55.320 --> 00:15:57.109
Thank you for being here.

00:15:57.109 --> 00:15:59.959
If you want to pray with me, fine.

00:15:59.959 --> 00:16:01.720
But this is what I see.

00:16:01.720 --> 00:16:05.753
Okay, so adding to and taking away from anything when you see...

00:16:15.994 --> 00:16:16.340
so here we are in October.

00:16:16.340 --> 00:16:19.519
Did we see any kind of big bubble bust?

00:16:19.519 --> 00:16:25.199
He said it was a mark in the spirit realm about October.

00:16:43.600 --> 00:16:44.100
And everybody says, "There's an October surprise.

00:16:44.100 --> 00:16:47.771
" I never heard the word "October surprise.

00:16:57.563 --> 00:16:57.848
" I never prophesied one time on my channel that there would be an October surprise.

00:16:57.848 --> 00:17:03.429
I said there would be an event that happens in October that would cause the economy to shake.

00:17:08.587 --> 00:17:10.068
The BRICS nations met and they had the major event around the 21st to the 24th.

00:17:10.068 --> 00:17:31.319
And so I believed in my spirit that that was the event because every single time I've seen and I've prayed, it's been around the BRICS creating, with China, Russia, Iran, Saudi Arabia, the petrodollar, all that stuff, creating their own currency, creating their own digital platform against the dollar, causing the dollar to crumble.

00:17:31.319 --> 00:17:33.320
That's what I've seen.

00:17:43.639 --> 00:17:47.120
And I've seen it completely destroy the dollar with having Saudi Arabia and the petrodollar joining up with China and all this other stuff.

00:17:59.679 --> 00:17:59.937
So when that happens, I still believe it because the Lord told me a house of cards will fall.

00:17:59.937 --> 00:18:06.152
And I saw the house of cards falling, and I saw a major shaking still taking place.

00:18:16.093 --> 00:18:16.547
And I saw the 1920s and 1930s and a major stock market crash similar to what happened.

00:18:22.017 --> 00:18:22.400
And then I saw the four oak trees.

00:18:23.516 --> 00:18:40.423
The Lord told me to pray about the four oak trees standing strong in this economic decision that will be made, which I believe is four years of President Trump's presidency—one, two, three, four years over the United States economy.

00:18:40.423 --> 00:18:46.740
So when you're seeing about the economy escalating and getting better for a small little window...

00:19:06.449 --> 00:19:07.189
what is it?

00:19:07.189 --> 00:19:09.114
A week, two weeks?

00:19:10.600 --> 00:19:10.920
I don't know.

00:19:10.920 --> 00:19:15.824
I'm learning to not try to say "this is what I feel.

00:19:15.824 --> 00:19:18.773
" No, this is what I saw.

00:19:18.773 --> 00:19:22.857
He did not give me a direct time frame yet.

00:19:22.857 --> 00:19:24.853
So I saw the economy...

00:19:24.853 --> 00:19:30.445
it could be just one day, it could be two days, it could be a week.

00:19:30.445 --> 00:19:31.450
Who knows?

00:19:33.200 --> 00:19:37.411
All I know is I saw the economy taking off for maybe a 24-hour window.

00:19:41.380 --> 00:19:41.640
I don't know.

00:19:41.640 --> 00:19:46.119
Because they announce that he wins, and then I saw Jerome Powell again.

00:19:46.119 --> 00:19:48.359
So Jerome Powell was still running things.

00:19:51.080 --> 00:19:52.076
And so I saw the house of cards fall.

00:19:52.076 --> 00:19:53.249
I saw the economy fall.

00:19:53.249 --> 00:19:57.223
Whether or not that is in January, I still saw the dam bursting.

00:19:57.223 --> 00:20:00.866
I still saw the terrible times ahead for the United States, a humbling coming.

00:20:02.749 --> 00:20:03.709
And people say, "What is the falling like gnats?

00:20:09.920 --> 00:20:10.200
" I saw the plague and I've warned you all about this plague.

00:20:10.200 --> 00:20:16.334
Donald Trump was president when the plague is released and he announces that he's shutting down air travel.

00:20:19.159 --> 00:20:22.710
And I saw a massive plague coming again that was worse than COVID on steroids.

00:20:33.359 --> 00:20:33.559
It was huge.

00:20:33.559 --> 00:20:36.628
From what I saw, 350 plus million people will perish.

00:20:37.942 --> 00:20:39.676
And I saw over 30 million in the United States of America.

00:20:41.268 --> 00:20:41.799
And it was very, very bad.

00:20:42.083 --> 00:20:46.411
And I saw people again, the Lord showed me, falling like gnats.

00:21:03.817 --> 00:21:04.183
And people around you that you thought were really, really strong Christians, and people that were walking a compromise.

00:21:11.395 --> 00:21:11.630
